attributes.title: Driver Memory
attributes.visState:
{"title":"Driver Memory","type":"timelion","params":{"expression":".es(q=driver.jvm.total.max:*,metric=avg:driver.jvm.total.max, split=applicationId.keyword:20,
timefield='timestamp').subtract(.es(q=driver.jvm.total.used:*,metric=avg:driver.jvm.total.used, split=applicationId.keyword:20,
timefield='timestamp')).yaxis(label="byte").label("Driver free mem@$1", "^.*applicationId.keyword:(.*) >(.*)").yaxis(min=0, label="MB").divide(1048576),

.es(q=driver.jvm.heap.used:*,metric=avg:driver.jvm.heap.used, split=applicationId.keyword:20,
timefield='timestamp').label("Driver heap used@$1", "^.*applicationId.keyword:(.*) >(.*)").yaxis(min=0, label="MB").divide(1048576),

.es(q=driver.jvm.heap.max:*,metric=avg:driver.jvm.heap.max, split=applicationId.keyword:20,
timefield='timestamp').label("Driver heap max@$1", "^.*applicationId.keyword:(.*) >(.*)").yaxis(min=0, label="MB").divide(1048576)","interval":"auto"},"aggs":[]}

attributes.title: Driver DAG Scheduler
attributes.visState:
{"aggs":[],"params":{"expression":".es(q=driver.CodeGenerator.generatedMethodSize.max:*,metric=max:driver.CodeGenerator.generatedMethodSize.max,split=applicationId.keyword:20,
timefield='timestamp').cusum().yaxis(label="Method size").label("Max method size@$1", "^.*applicationId.keyword:(.*) >(.*)"),
.es(q=driver.CodeGenerator.generatedMethodSize.mean:*,metric=avg:driver.CodeGenerator.generatedMethodSize.mean,split=applicationId.keyword:20,
timefield='timestamp').cusum().yaxis(label="Method size").label("Avg method size@$1", "^.*applicationId.keyword:(.*) >(.*)")","interval":"auto"},"title":"Driver DAG Scheduler","type":"timelion"}

attributes.title: Executors FS read / write
attributes.visState: {"title":"Executors FS read / write","type":"timelion","params":{"expression":".es(q=executor.filesystem.file.read_bytes:*,metric=sum:executor.filesystem.file.read_bytes, split=executorId.keyword:20,timefield='timestamp').derivative().scale_interval(1s).label(\"Executor $2@$1\", \"^.*executorId.keyword:(.*) >(.*)\").yaxis(label=\"bytes / sec\", units=bytes/s, min=0),\n.es(q=executor.filesystem.file.write_bytes:*,metric=sum:executor.filesystem.file.write_bytes, split=executorId.keyword:20,timefield='timestamp').derivative().scale_interval(1s).label(\"Executor $2@$1\", \"^.*executorId.keyword:(.*) >(.*)\").yaxis(label=\"bytes / sec\", units=bytes/s, min=0)","interval":"auto"},"aggs":[]}
